RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT COMPONENT,FEE_RULE ,(SELECT PAYMENT_TYPE_DESC FROM LBTM_FEE_COMPONENT_PYMNT_TYPE WHERE PAYMENT_TYPE =(SELECT PAYMENT_TYPE FROM LFTM_FEE_CLASS WHERE CLASS_CODE = A.COMPONENT AND MODULE='LB')) PAYMENT_TYPE,(SELECT FEE_BPS_RATE_APPLICABLE FROM LFTM_FEE_CLASS WHERE CLASS_CODE = A.COMPONENT AND MODULE='LB') FEE_BPS_RATE_APPLICABLE FROM LFTMS_PRODUCT_FEE A WHERE PRODUCT_CODE = ? AND NVL(STOP_ASSOCIATION,'N')='N' UNION SELECT COMPONENT,FEE_RULE ,(SELECT PAYMENT_TYPE_DESC FROM LBTM_FEE_COMPONENT_PYMNT_TYPE WHERE PAYMENT_TYPE =(SELECT PAYMENT_TYPE FROM LFTM_FEE_CLASS WHERE CLASS_CODE = B.COMPONENT AND MODULE='LB')) PAYMENT_TYPE,(SELECT FEE_BPS_RATE_APPLICABLE FROM LFTM_FEE_CLASS WHERE CLASS_CODE = B.COMPONENT AND MODULE='TC') FEE_BPS_RATE_APPLICABLE FROM LFTMS_PRODUCT_FEE B WHERE FEE_COLLECTION_MODE='D' AND PRODUCT_CODE= ? AND NVL(STOP_ASSOCIATION,'N')='N'

SELECT FEE_COMPONENT,DESCRIPTION FROM LFTMS_FEE_DEFINITION UNION SELECT RULE,DESCRIPTION FROM LFTMS_RULE WHERE CURRENCY = '*.*' AND CURRENCY2 = '*.*' AND CUSTOMER = 'ALL' AND CUST_GROUP='ALL' AND BRANCH='ALL'

SELECT VW.CCY_CODE, CCY.CCY_NAME FROM OLVWS_PRODUCT_CURRENCIES VW, CYTMS_CCY_DEFN CCY WHERE VW.CCY_CODE = CCY.CCY_CODE AND VW.PRODUCT_CODE = ? AND CCY.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND CCY.AUTH_STAT = 'A' ORDER BY VW.CCY_CODE

RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE.EVENT_SEQ_NO = LFTBS_FAS91_FEE_MASTER.EVENT_SEQ_NO AND LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE.COMPONENT = LFTBS_FAS91_FEE_MASTER.COMPONENT AND LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LFTBS_FAS91_FEE_MASTER.CONTRACT_REF_NO

LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE__MULTI.EVENT_SEQ_NO = LFTBS_FAS91_FEE_DETAIL__FAS.EVENT_SEQ_NO AND LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE__MULTI.COMPONENT = LFTBS_FAS91_FEE_DETAIL__FAS.COMPONENT AND LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE__MULTI.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LFTBS_FAS91_FEE_DETAIL__FAS.CONTRACT_REF_NO

LFTBS_FAS91_FEE_DETAIL__FAS.EVENT_SEQ_NO = LFTBS_FAS91_FEE_DETAIL.EVENT_SEQ_NO AND LFTBS_FAS91_FEE_DETAIL__FAS.COMPONENT = LFTBS_FAS91_FEE_DETAIL.COMPONENT AND LFTBS_FAS91_FEE_DETAIL__FAS.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LFTBS_FAS91_FEE_DETAIL.CONTRACT_REF_NO

LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE__MULTI.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LBTBS_PARTICIPANT_RATIO.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE__MULTI.COMPONENT = LBTBS_PARTICIPANT_RATIO.COMPONENT AND LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE__MULTI.EVENT_SEQ_NO = LBTBS_PARTICIPANT_RATIO.EVENT_SEQ_NO

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: select branch_code,branch_name from OLTMS_BRANCH where record_stat = 'O'

SELECT mis_code,code_desc FROM gltms_mis_code x,gltms_mis_class y WHERE x.mis_class = 'EXPCODE_T' AND x.active = 'A' AND y.mis_class = x.mis_class and mis_code not in (select mis_code from lftbs_fas91_fee_split_dtls where contract_ref_no = ? and component = ? and branch_code = ?) ORDER BY x.mis_code

select a.customer_no, a.customer_name1 from oltms_customer a, lbtbs_self_participant b where a.record_stat = 'O' and a.auth_stat = 'A' and a.customer_category = 'INVESTOR' and b.participant = a.customer_no and b.origination ='Y'
SELECT mis_code,code_desc FROM gltms_mis_code x,gltms_mis_class y WHERE x.mis_class = 'EXPCODE_T' AND x.active = 'A' AND y.mis_class = x.mis_class ORDER BY x.mis_code
select customer_no, customer_name1 from oltms_customer where once_auth='Y'
select ac_gl_no ,ac_gl_desc from oltbs_account where ac_gl_rec_status = 'O'
